*Naredniče*, nastavi svoj put! (Go ahead, *officer*!)

*Naredniče*, ti si na čelu! (You are in charge, *officer*!)

Čast nam je što nam je *naredniče* pomogao. (We are honored that *the officer* has helped us.)

*Naredniče* je odmah reagovao. (*The officer* reacted immediately.)

*Naredniče* je veoma poštovan čovek. (*The officer* is a very respected man.)